<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About Project</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap -->
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-light">

<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="bg-primary text-white py-5">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">About This Project</h2>
    <p class="opacity-75 mb-0">
      Patient Queue Management System
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">

  <!-- PROBLEM STATEMENT -->
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2">📌 Problem Statement</h4>
    <p class="text-muted">
      In many clinics and hospitals, patients wait for long hours without knowing
      how many people are ahead of them or how much time it will take. Queue handling
      is usually manual, which causes confusion, overcrowding, and repeated questions
      at the reception desk.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- SOLUTION -->
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2">💡 Our Solution</h4>
    <p class="text-muted">
      This project provides a digital token-based queue system where patients can
      check their queue position, number of patients ahead, and estimated waiting
      time using a simple token number.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT HELPS -->
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2">🩺 How It Helps</h4>
    <ul class="text-muted">
      <li>Patients get clear visibility of their queue status</li>
      <li>Reduces unnecessary crowding at the clinic</li>
      <li>Reception staff spend less time answering queue-related questions</li>
      <li>Improves overall patient experience</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- ADVANTAGES -->
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2">✅ Key Advantages</h4>
    <ul class="text-muted">
      <li>Simple and easy to use interface</li>
      <li>Accurate queue tracking using token numbers</li>
      <li>Estimated waiting time calculation</li>
      <li>Eliminates manual queue errors</li>
      <li>Scalable for future enhancements</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- TECHNOLOGY -->
  <div>
    <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-2">🛠 Technology Used</h4>
    <p class="text-muted mb-0">
      Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose, EJS, Bootstrap
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

<script
  src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js">
</script>

</body>
</html>
